"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-31-scary-moment-gymnast-goes-flying-equipment-malfunction-olympics-21337443\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Canadian gymnast Felix Dolci suffered a scary moment at theOlympicsafter an 'equipment malfunction' sent him flying off the horizontal bar and crashing into the floor.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9864305893752549, \"rank\": 0.013620212225849679, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 22, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\", \"score\": 0.9996064161746752, \"rank\": 0.00036348905161185784, \"text\": \"Felix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dolci was into his final few apparatus in the men's all-round gymnastics final when he suffered a huge and nasty fall on the bars.\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old made a strong start to his routine and was picking up speed when his handguard split, causing him to lose grip and go flying.\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Momentum sent Dolci into a somersault before he crashed into the safety mat, prompting audible gasps from the fans inside the Bercy Arena and the BBC commentary team.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 590, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.86747891341042, \"rank\": 0.1526934371052931, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Oh dear!\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'BBCcommentator Matt Baker exclaimed after the scary incident.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Baker_(artist)\", \"score\": 0.9803545262364683, \"rank\": 0.016653655997920964, \"text\": \"Matt Baker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Baker_(artist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Baker_(artist)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'His handguard has split.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Well, goodness me.\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was lucky there because that could have caused himself a very, very nasty injury.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully he's alright.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 839, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What an unbelievable shock.'\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dolci understandably looked shocked as he gathered his composure on the floor as members of the Canadian coaching team came over to check in on him.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9864305893752549, \"rank\": 0.013620212225849679, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now this is something you do not see every day \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u00aeThankfully Canadian gymnast Felix Dolci is OK.#BBCOlympics#Olympics#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/wQR07cy8mo  After taking a few seconds to catch his breath, Dolci confirmed to his team that he was okay, though he sported a nasty cut on his right hand that hampered the rest of his performance.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1082, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9864305893752549, \"rank\": 0.013620212225849679, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\", \"score\": 0.9996064161746752, \"rank\": 0.00036348905161185784, \"text\": \"Felix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather impressively, Dolci then found a new set of handguards and resumed his routine.\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Huge respect on every level for Felix Dolci,' Baker added.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\", \"score\": 0.9996064161746752, \"rank\": 0.00036348905161185784, \"text\": \"Felix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\"}, {\"begin\": 1497, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baker\", \"score\": 0.9999964031181776, \"rank\": 3.551194617398918e-06, \"text\": \"Baker\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'His competition was going so, so well.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1550, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is so unlucky for him [that he fell].\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What a shame.'\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Commonwealth Games gold winner Craig Heap added: 'As a gymnast there is so much force through the hands and the guards.\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1608, \"end\": 1626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2006_Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.6021435074840125, \"rank\": 0.6453676754929972, \"text\": \"Commonwealth Games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2006_Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2006_Commonwealth_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1639, \"end\": 1649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Heap\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Craig Heap\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Heap\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Heap\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You go through a set of guards every couple of months.\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I always had a spare pair of guards in my bag just in case.'\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A nasty moment for Jesse Moore on the horizontal bar.\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a4\\u0095Thankfully, the Australian is fine to continue.#BBCOlympics#Olympics#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/vhuCA9V6BJ  Dolci was not the only gymnast to suffer a nasty fall in the Olympic final, with Australia's Jesse Moore also hitting the deck after a mistake on the horizontal bar.\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9935060986143299, \"rank\": 0.0055553709074458585, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2092, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9858662374917683, \"rank